      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
