    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is in peak form; a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized dealerships accompanies the sale. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car is for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. Pre-purchase inspections are welcomed and encouraged to verify this vehicle's peerless state.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
